data.title: 2022-23 Annual Report
data.meta_description: Annual Report 2022-’23 Dear Jayhawks, The Alumni Association takes great pride in uniting and building relationships among our global community of 380,000 alumni, and we are dedicated to carrying forward the tradition of excellence that has defined generations of Jayhawks. Our loyal and engaged alumni form the cornerstone of your vibrant alumni association, which serves […]
